HEADWORD: Two-port
<hw>Two"-port`</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having two ports; specif.:
Designating a type of two-cycle internal-combustion engine in which the
admission of the mixture to the crank case is through a suction
valve.</def>⟦br⟧
